title: My Way to the Stars
info:
Originally featured on Party Demo (Demo) by Double Density Crew released on the Amiga in January 1989.

[url]http://janeway.exotica.org.uk/release.php?id=771[/url]

The module was also ported to the Acorn Archimedes and featured in the Brothers in ARM demo !Sister.. 

[yt]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iCdc0ATVgLQ[/yt]

The demo featured a SoundTracker playroutine written in ARM assembler by Hugo Fiennes which was the first to be written on the Archimedes platform.

Many years later Hugo went on to head the iPhone 4 hardware design team at Apple!!
